snippet.title: DemonriftTD video
snippet.description:
Demonrift TD is an old school Tower Defense Game with a very thick RPG element inside. 

The game revolves around One HERO and 4 different tower types and each of them must kept buffed up in a purely Role Playing Games way by replaying levels and purchasing equipments.
